%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: ef4120e8d7cc4784ba80e7aeb2d6d58d, type: 3}
  m_Name: Runestone_MurderOfBaldur
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  Repeatable: 1
  Lines:
  - Text: 'This runestone contains a story. It reads as follows:'
    Speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6386bee0cce89a84f80df160c871f056, type: 2}
  - Text: "Beloved children three, of the trickster god were they.\r\nThe all-father
      saw them play, the future they would bring.\r\nThe wolf that eats the sun,
      the snake of thunder\u2019s decay.\r\nCast out for crimes uncommitted, for
      futures yet to sing."
    Speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6386bee0cce89a84f80df160c871f056, type: 2}
  - Text: 'Chained with impossibility, the great beast quelling.

      Cast to the
      cold-black ocean, the serpent left to grow.

      The last sister fair, given
      death for dwelling.

      Mistress of the fallen, crowned in dusk and snow.'
    Speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6386bee0cce89a84f80df160c871f056, type: 2}
  - Text: What father would not remember? What god would not take heed?
    Speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6386bee0cce89a84f80df160c871f056, type: 2}
  - Text: 'Then Baldur dreamed of dying; bright Baldur, beloved of all.

      So
      fair all things forget their thirst for blood.

      The bright god fell,
      and all of Asgard looked on in appall.

      And the Father of Lies laughed
      right where he stood.'
    Speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6386bee0cce89a84f80df160c871f056, type: 2}
  - Text: 'Was it hatred for the shining, envy of the adored?

      Was it grief
      that curdled inward, made venom of his love?

      For every cheer that hailed
      Baldur rang like striking from a sword.

      On the chains that bit his children,
      far below, far above.'
    Speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6386bee0cce89a84f80df160c871f056, type: 2}
  - Text: Such it is that trickster gods love, and lovely gods trick.
    Speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6386bee0cce89a84f80df160c871f056, type: 2}
  OnFinished:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
